    "html": "<div class=\"B1_text_xin\" id=\"cont\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img alt=\"\\\" src=\"https://www.liaotuo.com/uploadfile/2016/0123/20160123052937794.jpg\" style=\"height: 280px; width: 207px;\" /></p>\n<h3>（如发现注音有错误，请您联系我们，便于我们及时纠正，QQ：1300659095。<a href=\"/remen/ganen.html\" class=\"keylink\" target=\"_blank\">感恩</a>）</h3>\n<p><span>wéi<br />&#13;\n为</span><span>fó<br />&#13;\n佛</span><span>dì<br />&#13;\n弟</span><span>zǐ<br />&#13;\n子</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>cháng<br />&#13;\n常</span><span>yú<br />&#13;\n于</span><span>zhò u<br />&#13;\n昼</span><span>yè<br />&#13;\n夜</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>zhì<br />&#13;\n至</span><span>xīn<br />&#13;\n心</span><span>sòng<br />&#13;\n诵</span><span>nìan<br />&#13;\n念</span><span>bā<br />&#13;\n八 </span><span>dà<br />&#13;\n大</span><span>rén<br />&#13;\n人</span><span>jué<br />&#13;\n觉</span><span>：<br />&#13;\n：</span></p>\n<p><span>dì<br />&#13;\n第</span><span>yī<br />&#13;\n一</span><span>jué<br />&#13;\n觉</span><span>wù<br />&#13;\n悟</span><span>：<br />&#13;\n：</span><span>shì<br />&#13;\n世</span><span>jiān<br />&#13;\n间 </span><span>wú<br />&#13;\n无</span><span>cháng<br />&#13;\n常</span><span>；<br />&#13;\n；</span><span>guó<br />&#13;\n国</span><span>tǔ<br />&#13;\n土</span><span>wēi<br />&#13;\n危</span><span>cuì<br />&#13;\n脆 </span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>sì<br />&#13;\n四</span><span>dà<br />&#13;\n大</span><span>kǔ<br />&#13;\n苦</span><span>kōng<br />&#13;\n空</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>wǔ<br />&#13;\n五</span><span>y īn<br />&#13;\n阴</span><span>wú<br />&#13;\n无</span><span>wǒ<br />&#13;\n我</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>shēng<br />&#13;\n生</span><span>mìe<br />&#13;\n灭</span><span>bìan<br />&#13;\n变</span><span>yì<br />&#13;\n异 </span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>xū<br />&#13;\n虚</span><span>wěi<br />&#13;\n伪</span><span>wú<br />&#13;\n无</span><span>zhǔ<br />&#13;\n主</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>xīn<br />&#13;\n心 </span><span>shì<br />&#13;\n是</span><span>è<br />&#13;\n恶</span><span>yuán<br />&#13;\n源</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>xíng<br />&#13;\n形</span><span>wéi<br />&#13;\n为</span><span>zuì<br />&#13;\n罪 </span><span>sǒu<br />&#13;\n薮</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>rú<br />&#13;\n如</span><span>shì<br />&#13;\n是</span><span>guān<br />&#13;\n观</span><span>chá<br />&#13;\n察</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n， </span><span>jiàn<br />&#13;\n渐</span><span>lí<br />&#13;\n离</span><span>shēng<br />&#13;\n生</span><span>sǐ<br />&#13;\n死</span><span>。<br />&#13;\n。</span></p>\n<p><span>dì<br />&#13;\n第</span><span>èr<br />&#13;\n二</span><span>jué<br />&#13;\n觉</span><span>zhī<br />&#13;\n知</span><span>：<br />&#13;\n：</span><span>duō<br />&#13;\n多</span><span>yù<br />&#13;\n欲 </span><span>wéi<br />&#13;\n为</span><span>kǔ<br />&#13;\n苦</span><span>；<br />&#13;\n；</span><span>shēng<br />&#13;\n生</span><span>sǐ<br />&#13;\n死</span><span>pí<br />&#13;\n疲</span><span>láo<br />&#13;\n劳 </span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>cóng<br />&#13;\n从</span><span>tān<br />&#13;\n贪</span><span>yù<br />&#13;\n欲</span><span>qǐ<br />&#13;\n起</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>shǎo<br />&#13;\n少 </span><span>yù<br />&#13;\n欲</span><span>wú<br />&#13;\n无</span><span>wéi<br />&#13;\n为</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>shēn<br />&#13;\n身</span><span>xīn<br />&#13;\n心</span><span>zì<br />&#13;\n自 </span><span>zài<br />&#13;\n在</span><span>；<br />&#13;\n；</span></p>\n<p><span>dì<br />&#13;\n第</span><span>sān<br />&#13;\n三</span><span>jué<br />&#13;\n觉</span><span>zhī<br />&#13;\n知</span><span>：<br />&#13;\n：</span><span>xīn<br />&#13;\n心</span><span>wú<br />&#13;\n无 </span><span>yàn<br />&#13;\n厌</span><span>zú<br />&#13;\n足</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>wéi<br />&#13;\n惟</span><span>dé<br />&#13;\n得</span><span>duō<br />&#13;\n多</span><span>qiú<br />&#13;\n求 </span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>zēng<br />&#13;\n增</span><span>zhǎng<br />&#13;\n长</span><span>zuì<br />&#13;\n罪</span><span>è<br />&#13;\n恶</span><span>；<br />&#13;\n；</span><span>pǘ<br />&#13;\n菩 </span><span>sà<br />&#13;\n萨</span><span>bù<br />&#13;\n不</span><span>ěr<br />&#13;\n尔</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>cháng<br />&#13;\n常</span><span>nìan<br />&#13;\n念</span><span>zhī<br />&#13;\n知 </span><span>zú<br />&#13;\n足</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>ān<br />&#13;\n安</span><span>pín<br />&#13;\n贫</span><span>shǒu<br />&#13;\n守</span><span>dào<br />&#13;\n道</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n， </span><span>wéi<br />&#13;\n惟</span><span>huì<br />&#13;\n慧</span><span>shì<br />&#13;\n是</span><span>yè<br />&#13;\n业</span><span>。<br />&#13;\n。</span></p>\n<p><span>dì<br />&#13;\n第</span><span>sì<br />&#13;\n四</span><span>jué<br />&#13;\n觉</span><span>zhī<br />&#13;\n知</span><span>：<br />&#13;\n：</span><span>xiè<br />&#13;\n懈</span><span>dài<br />&#13;\n怠</span><span>zhu ì<br />&#13;\n坠</span><span>luò<br />&#13;\n落</span><span>；<br />&#13;\n；</span><span>cháng<br />&#13;\n常</span><span>xíng<br />&#13;\n行</span><span>jīng<br />&#13;\n精</span><span>jìn<br />&#13;\n进</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>pò<br />&#13;\n破</span><span>fán<br />&#13;\n烦</span><span>nǎo<br />&#13;\n恼</span><span>è<br />&#13;\n恶</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>cuī<br />&#13;\n摧</span><span>fú<br />&#13;\n伏 </span><span>sì<br />&#13;\n四</span><span>mó<br />&#13;\n魔</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>chū<br />&#13;\n出</span><span>yīn<br />&#13;\n阴</span><span>jiè<br />&#13;\n界</span><span>yù<br />&#13;\n狱</span><span> 。<br />&#13;\n。</span></p>\n<p><span>dì<br />&#13;\n第</span><span>wǔ<br />&#13;\n五</span><span>jué<br />&#13;\n觉</span><span>wù<br />&#13;\n悟</span><span>：<br />&#13;\n：</span><span>yú<br />&#13;\n愚</span><span>chī<br />&#13;\n痴 </span><span>shēng<br />&#13;\n生</span><span>sǐ<br />&#13;\n死</span><span>；<br />&#13;\n；</span><span>pú<br />&#13;\n菩</span><span>sà<br />&#13;\n萨</span><span>cháng<br />&#13;\n常</span><span>niàn<br />&#13;\n念 </span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>guǎng<br />&#13;\n广</span><span>xué<br />&#13;\n学</span><span>duō<br />&#13;\n多</span><span>wén<br />&#13;\n闻</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>zēng<br />&#13;\n增 </span><span>zhǎng<br />&#13;\n长</span><span>zhì<br />&#13;\n智</span><span>huì<br />&#13;\n慧</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>chéng<br />&#13;\n成</span><span>jiù<br />&#13;\n就</span><span>biàn<br />&#13;\n辩 </span><span>cái<br />&#13;\n才</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>jiào<br />&#13;\n教</span><span>huà<br />&#13;\n化</span><span>yī<br />&#13;\n一</span><span>qiè<br />&#13;\n切</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n， </span><span>xī<br />&#13;\n悉</span><span>yǐ<br />&#13;\n以</span><span>dà<br />&#13;\n大</span><span>lè<br />&#13;\n乐</span><br />&#13;\n </p>\n<p><span>dì<br />&#13;\n第</span><span>liù<br />&#13;\n六</span><span>jué<br />&#13;\n觉</span><span>zhī<br />&#13;\n知</span><span>：<br />&#13;\n：</span><span>pín<br />&#13;\n贫</span><span>kǔ<br />&#13;\n苦</span><span>duō<br />&#13;\n多</span><span>yuàn<br />&#13;\n怨</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>héng<br />&#13;\n横</span><span>jié<br />&#13;\n结</span><span>è<br />&#13;\n恶</span><span>yuán<br />&#13;\n缘</span><span>；<br />&#13;\n； </span><span>pú<br />&#13;\n菩</span><span>sà<br />&#13;\n萨</span><span>bù<br />&#13;\n布</span><span>shī<br />&#13;\n施</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>děng<br />&#13;\n等</span><span>nìan<br />&#13;\n念 </span><span>yuàn<br />&#13;\n怨</span><span>qīn<br />&#13;\n亲</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>bú<br />&#13;\n不</span><span>niàn<br />&#13;\n念</span><span>jiù<br />&#13;\n旧</span><span>è<br />&#13;\n恶 </span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>bú<br />&#13;\n不</span><span>zēng<br />&#13;\n憎</span><span>wù<br />&#13;\n恶</span><span>rén<br />&#13;\n人</span><span>。<br />&#13;\n。</span></p>\n<p><span>dì<br />&#13;\n第</span><span>qī<br />&#13;\n七</span><span>jué<br />&#13;\n觉</span><span>wù<br />&#13;\n悟</span><span>：<br />&#13;\n：</span><span>wǔ<br />&#13;\n五</span><span>yù<br />&#13;\n欲</span><span>guò<br />&#13;\n过</span><span>huàn<br />&#13;\n患</span><span>；<br />&#13;\n；</span><span>suī<br />&#13;\n虽</span><span>wéi<br />&#13;\n为</span><span>sú<br />&#13;\n俗</span><span>rén<br />&#13;\n人</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n， </span><span>bù<br />&#13;\n不</span><span>rǎn<br />&#13;\n染</span><span>shì<br />&#13;\n世</span><span>lè<br />&#13;\n乐</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>cháng<br />&#13;\n常</span><span>niàn<br />&#13;\n念 </span><span>sān<br />&#13;\n三</span><span>yī<br />&#13;\n衣</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>wǎ<br />&#13;\n瓦</span><span>bō<br />&#13;\n钵</span><span>fǎ<br />&#13;\n法</span><span>qì<br />&#13;\n器</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>zhì<br />&#13;\n志</span><span>yuàn<br />&#13;\n愿</span><span>chū<br />&#13;\n出</span><span>jiā<br />&#13;\n家</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>shǒu<br />&#13;\n守</span><span>dào<br />&#13;\n道 </span><span>qīng<br />&#13;\n清</span><span>bái<br />&#13;\n白</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>fàn<br />&#13;\n梵</span><span>xíng<br />&#13;\n行</span><span>gāo<br />&#13;\n高</span><span>yuǎn<br />&#13;\n远 </span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>cí<br />&#13;\n慈</span><span>bēi<br />&#13;\n悲</span><span>yī<br />&#13;\n一</span><span>qiè<br />&#13;\n切</span><span>。<br />&#13;\n。</span></p>\n<p><span>dì<br />&#13;\n第</span><span>bā<br />&#13;\n八</span><span>jué<br />&#13;\n觉</span><span>zhī<br />&#13;\n知</span><span>：<br />&#13;\n：</span><span>shēng<br />&#13;\n生</span><span>sǐ<br />&#13;\n死</span><span>chì<br />&#13;\n炽</span><span>rán<br />&#13;\n然</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>kǔ<br />&#13;\n苦</span><span>nǎo<br />&#13;\n恼</span><span>wú<br />&#13;\n无</span><span>liàng<br />&#13;\n量</span><span>；<br />&#13;\n；</span><span>fā<br />&#13;\n发</span><span>dà<br />&#13;\n大</span><span>chéng<br />&#13;\n乘</span><span>xīn<br />&#13;\n心</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>pǔ<br />&#13;\n普</span><span>jì<br />&#13;\n济</span><span>yī<br />&#13;\n一</span><span>qiè<br />&#13;\n切</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>yuàn<br />&#13;\n愿</span><span>dài<br />&#13;\n代</span><span>zhòng<br />&#13;\n众</span><span>shēng<br />&#13;\n生</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>shòu<br />&#13;\n受</span><span>wú<br />&#13;\n无</span><span>liàng<br />&#13;\n量</span><span>kǔ<br />&#13;\n苦</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>lìng<br />&#13;\n令</span><span>zhū<br />&#13;\n诸</span><span>zhòng<br />&#13;\n众</span><span>shēng<br />&#13;\n生</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>bì<br />&#13;\n毕</span><span>jìng<br />&#13;\n竟</span><span>dà<br />&#13;\n大</span><span>lè<br />&#13;\n乐</span><span>。<br />&#13;\n。</span></p>\n<p><span>rú<br />&#13;\n如</span><span>cǐ<br />&#13;\n此</span><span>bā<br />&#13;\n八</span><span>shì<br />&#13;\n事</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>nǎi<br />&#13;\n乃</span><span>shì<br />&#13;\n是</span><span>zhū<br />&#13;\n诸</span><span>fó<br />&#13;\n佛</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>pú<br />&#13;\n菩</span><span>sà<br />&#13;\n萨</span><span>dà<br />&#13;\n大</span><span>rén<br />&#13;\n人</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>zhī<br />&#13;\n之</span><span>suǒ<br />&#13;\n所</span><span>jué<br />&#13;\n觉</span><span>wù<br />&#13;\n悟</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>jīng<br />&#13;\n精</span><span>jìn<br />&#13;\n进</span><span>xíng<br />&#13;\n行</span><span>dào<br />&#13;\n道</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>cí<br />&#13;\n慈</span><span>bēi<br />&#13;\n悲</span><span>xiū<br />&#13;\n修</span><span>huì<br />&#13;\n慧</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>chéng<br />&#13;\n乘</span><span>fǎ<br />&#13;\n法</span><span>shēn<br />&#13;\n身</span><span>chuán<br />&#13;\n船</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>zhì<br />&#13;\n至</span><span>niè<br />&#13;\n涅</span><span>pán<br />&#13;\n槃</span><span>àn<br />&#13;\n岸</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>fù<br />&#13;\n复</span><span>hái<br />&#13;\n还</span><span>shēng<br />&#13;\n生</span><span>sǐ<br />&#13;\n死</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>dù<br />&#13;\n度</span><span>tuō<br />&#13;\n脱</span><span>zhòng<br />&#13;\n众</span><span>shēng<br />&#13;\n生</span><span>。<br />&#13;\n。</span><span>yǐ<br />&#13;\n以</span><span>qián<br />&#13;\n前</span><span>bā<br />&#13;\n八</span><span>shì<br />&#13;\n事</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>kāi<br />&#13;\n开</span><span>dǎo<br />&#13;\n导</span><span>yī<br />&#13;\n一</span><span>qiè<br />&#13;\n切</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>lìng<br />&#13;\n令</span><span>zhū<br />&#13;\n诸</span><span>zhòng<br />&#13;\n众</span><span>shēng<br />&#13;\n生</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>jué<br />&#13;\n觉</span><span>shēng<br />&#13;\n生</span><span>sǐ<br />&#13;\n死</span><span>kǔ<br />&#13;\n苦</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>shě<br />&#13;\n舍</span><span>lí<br />&#13;\n离</span><span>wǔ<br />&#13;\n五</span><span>yù<br />&#13;\n欲</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>xiū<br />&#13;\n修</span><span>xīn<br />&#13;\n心</span><span>shèng<br />&#13;\n圣</span><span>dào<br />&#13;\n道</span><span>。<br />&#13;\n。</span><span>ruò<br />&#13;\n若</span><span>fó<br />&#13;\n佛</span><span>dì<br />&#13;\n弟</span><span>zǐ<br />&#13;\n子</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>sòng<br />&#13;\n诵</span><span>cǐ<br />&#13;\n此</span><span>bā<br />&#13;\n八</span><span>shì<br />&#13;\n事</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>yú<br />&#13;\n于</span><span>niàn<br />&#13;\n念</span><span>niàn<br />&#13;\n念</span><span>zhōng<br />&#13;\n中</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>miè<br />&#13;\n灭</span><span>wú<br />&#13;\n无</span><span>liàng<br />&#13;\n量</span><br />\n<span>zuì<br />&#13;\n罪</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>jìn<br />&#13;\n进</span><span>qù<br />&#13;\n趣</span><span>pú<br />&#13;\n菩</span><span>tí<br />&#13;\n提</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>sù<br />&#13;\n速</span><span>dēng<br />&#13;\n登</span><span>zhèng<br />&#13;\n正</span><span>jué<br />&#13;\n觉</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>yǒng<br />&#13;\n永</span><span>duàn<br />&#13;\n断</span><span>shēng<br />&#13;\n生</span><span>sǐ<br />&#13;\n死</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>cháng<br />&#13;\n常</span><span>zhù<br />&#13;\n住</span><span>kuài<br />&#13;\n快</span><span>lè<br />&#13;\n乐</span><span>。<br />&#13;\n。</span></p>\n</div>"
